== What is po-backend
'po-backend' is a DRb service that provides a Ruby interface to
Pology (for checking translation files using custom rules) and
Gettext (for checking translation file for validity).

== How to start the DRb service
You can either run po-backend as a console application:
 ./server.rb

or start/stop it as a daemon:
 ./server_control.rb start
 ./server_control.rb stop
